dct_title_s: Map of Ann Arbor showing campus and buildings of the University of Michigan prepared by Wickes Brothers.
dct_description_sm: Concentric radii drawn every quarter-mile. Verso: Key to University and other buildings, description of University buildings, and a bird's-eye view of the campus. MiU copy mounted on chartex. 1 map.: 44 x 36 cm.
dct_rights_sm: This map is in the public domain.
